  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safe Water and Good Hygiene Campaign in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is intended to enhance the health status and productivity of  vulnerable communities  in Nangabo Sub-county,Central Uganda. These  communities rely mainly on unprotected springs as a source of water as the safe water coverage is  49% . The water is usually full of diseases causing germs. Worse still the sanitation conditions and hygiene practices in  the household /schools, are  inadequate. This project will ensure access to safe and clean water as well as better hygiene practices</narrative>
  </description>
